messages.ssml:
<speak>
  Hey! I'm here to help you! 
  <break time="1000ms"/>
  You can try a lot of things on Hostel Chef.
  
  <prosody rate="slow">It is very simple and easy to use.</prosody>
  
	<break time="500ms"/>
  Want to know what is in breakfast today?
  <break time="500ms"/>
  Try saying, 
  <prosody volume="loud">What's in the breakfast today?.</prosody>
  <prosody rate="fast">try them out for lunch, snacks and dinner.</prosody>
  
  To get Girl's Hostel specific Menu,
  <break time="500ms"/>
  Try saying, 
  <prosody volume="loud">Breakfast today for girls?.</prosody>
  
  <break time="1000ms"/>
  To know what is in the lunch tomorrow or day after?
  <break time="500ms"/>
  Try saying, 
  <prosody volume="loud">What's in the lunch tomorrow?.</prosody>
  <prosody rate="slow">or</prosody>
  <prosody >day after?</prosody>
  
  <break time="1000ms"/>
  To know what is in the dinner on Friday?
  <break time="500ms"/>
  Try saying, 
  <prosody volume="loud">What's in the dinner on Friday?.</prosody>
  
  <prosody rate="slow">It is as simple as this!.</prosody>
  
  <break time="1000ms"/>
  To know when is milk served?
  <break time="500ms"/>
  Try saying, 
  <prosody volume="loud">When is milk served?.</prosody>
  <prosody rate="fast">or simply say.</prosody>
  <prosody rate="slow">Milk.</prosody>
  
  
  <prosody pitch="low">Just say anything and we will be back will a savage response a day after.</prosody>
  <prosody rate="slow">Hostel Chef, </prosody><break time="500ms"/>
  <prosody rate="fast">I'll be right here when you need me. </prosody>
</speak>
messages.displayText:
Hey I'm here to help you!
You can try a lot of things on Hostel Chef.
It is very simple and easy to use.

Want to know what is in breakfast today? 
Try saying, 
"What's in the breakfast today?"
 try them out for lunch, snacks & dinner. 

To get Girl's Hostel specific Menu, 
Try saying, 
"Breakfast today for girls?"

To know what is in the lunch tomorrow or day after?
Try saying, 
"What's in the lunch tomorrow?" or "day after?"

To know what is in the dinner on Friday? 
Try saying, 
"What's in the dinner on Friday?"

It is as simple as this!

To know when is milk served? 
Try saying, 
"When is milk served?" or simply say, "Milk".
  
  
Hostel Chef, 
I'll be right here when you need me.
